<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-bs-theme="dark">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>lolbot control — setup required</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="container" style="max-width:420px;margin-top:60px">
  <h1 class="h3 mb-3">lolbot control — setup required</h1>
  <div class="alert alert-danger py-2 mb-3">No <code>control_key</code> is configured.</div>
  <p>The panel and the bot's live-control endpoints both require a <code>control_key</code>.</p>
  <ol>
    <li>Add a key to <code>config.yaml</code>:<br>
        <code>control_key: "your-secret-key"</code></li>
    <li>Restart the bot (<code>php lolbot.php</code>) so it picks up the key for <code>/_control/*</code>.</li>
    <li>Reload this page — you'll get a login prompt. Enter the key.</li>
  </ol>
  <p class="text-body-secondary">The key is the panel login password and the auth token the panel sends to the running bot.</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
